get_interactiv...nstraint_modes(25.10)  get_interactiv...nstraint_modes(25.10)

Name
       get_interactive_constraint_modes

Syntax
        get_interactive_constraint_modes

       [-help]

       Returns a list of the multi-mode multi-corner constraint modes that are
       in interactive constraint entry mode.

       When the software is in interactive constraint entry mode (set_interac-
       tive_constraint_modes),  any timing constraints you specify take effect
       immediately on all active analysis views that are associated with these
       constraint modes.

       Note: Interactive constraint mode only works when the  software  is  in
       multi-mode multi-corner timing analysis mode.

Related Information
              * set_interactive_constraint_modes

